am H. Pauley III]] (A.B. 1974, J.D. 1977), [[United States federal judge|judge]], [[United States District Court for the Southern District of New York]]\n*[[Cary Douglas Pugh]] (A.B. 1987), [[United States federal judge|judge]], [[United States Tax Court]]\n*[[Robin L. Rosenberg]] (J.D. 1989), [[United States District Judge|Judge]], [[United States District Court for the Southern District of Florida]]\n*[[Gary Stein (New Jersey Supreme Court Justice)|Gary Stein]] (A.B. 1954, J.D. 1956), former associate justice, [[New Jersey Supreme Court]]\n*[[Allison Jones Rushing]] (J.D. 2007), nominee to be a [[United States Circuit Judge]] of the [[United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit]]\n*[[John J. Tharp, Jr.]] (A.B. 1982), [[United States federal judge|judge]], [[United States District Court for the Northern District of Illinois]]\n*[[Michael B. Thornton]] (J.D. 1982), former chief [[United States federal judge|judge]], [[United States Tax Court]]\n*[[Patricia Timmons-Goodson]] (LL.M. 2014), former associate justice, [[North Carolina Supreme Court]]\n*[[Gerald B. Tjoflat]] (LL.B. 1957), [[United States federal judge|chief judge emeritus]], [[U.S. Court of Appeals for the 11th Circuit]]\n*[[John M. Tyson]] (M.B.A. 1988), judge, [[North Carolina Court of Appeals]]\n*[[Peter Verniero]] (J.D. 1984), associate justice, [[New Jersey Supreme Court]]; former [[New Jersey Attorney General|Attorney General of New Jersey]]\n*[[Justin R. Walker]] (A.B. 2004), nominee to be a [[United States District Judge]] of the [[Western District of Kentucky]]\n*[[Charles K. Wiggins]] (J.D. 1976), justice, [[Washington Supreme Court]]\n*[[Don Willett]] (A.M. 1992, J.D. 1992), judge, [[U.S. Court of Appeals for the 5th Circuit]]\n\n=====Attorneys=====\n*[[Ward Armstrong]] (B.A. 1977), lawyer and politician\n*[[Charlie Condon]] (J.D. 1978), former Attorney General of South Carolina\n*[[Jack Conway (politician)|Jack Conway]] (A.B. 1991), Attorney General of [[Kentucky]]\n*[[Marc Elias]] (