ember states of the United Nations]]\n[[Category:Middle Eastern countries]]\n[[Category:Member states of the Turkic Council]]\n[[Category:Near Eastern countries]]\n[[Category:Republics]]\n[[Category:States and territories established in 1923]]\n[[Category:Western Asian countries]]\n[[Category:1923 establishments in Turkey]]\n[[Category:1923 establishments in Asia]]\n[[Category:Countries in Asia]]\n[[Category:Turkish-speaking countries and territories]]\n[[Category:Countries in Europe|Turkey]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Country in Western Asia with a small portion in Southeastern Europe}}\n{{about|the country|the bird|Turkey (bird)|other uses}} <!-- Here add only the other articles titled Turkey -->\n{{redir|T\u00fcrkiye|the newspaper|T\u00fcrkiye (newspaper)}} <!-- Here add only the other articles titled T\u00fcrkiye -->\n{{pp-vandalism|small=yes}}\n{{EngvarB|date=November 2019}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox country\n| conventional_long_name     = Republic of Turkey\n| common_name                = Turkey\n| native_name                = {{native name|tr|T\u00fcrkiye Cumhuriyeti}}\n| image_flag                 = Flag of Turkey.svg\n| image_coat                 = <!-- The Turkish Constitution doesn't specify an official coat of arms -->\n| national_motto             = <!-- The Turkish Constitution doesn't specify an official motto -->\n| national_anthem            = <br />{{vunblist |\"[[\u0130stiklal Mar\u015f\u0131]]\" |{{small|\"The Independence March\"}}|[[File:IstiklalMarsi-2013.ogg|center]]}}\n| image_map                  = Turkey (orthographic projection).svg\n| capital                    = [[Ankara]]\n| coordinates                = {{Coord|40|N|33|E|type:city|display=title,inline}}\n| largest_city               = [[Istanbul]]<br />{{smaller|{{coord|41|1|N|28|57|E|display=inline}}}}\n| official_languages         = [[Turkish language|Turkish]]\n| languages_type             = [[Spoken language]]s<ref name=Ethnologue>[[Ethnologue]]: [http